lead_paragraph: Tottenham Hotspur's Christian Eriksen said his "closed-eye" goal against Swansea City was among his best for the club and that it was more pleasing than the one he scored against Chelsea.

headline.print_headline: Shut-Eye Goal Against Swansea Among Eriksen's Favourites
